It now seems the XP at lvl 60 given from mobs that are level 55 is almost twice that of XP from mobs that are level 54.<br>
<br>
Does it not seem reasonable that we need the /con system updated to reflect this.<br>
<br>
If a level 60 is to /con a mob in the 55 to 59 range another colour should be shown to represent that this is a &quot;choice&quot; target. Purple con perhaps.<br>
<br>
